item.title: Description Of Operating System
item.description: Introduction: We are making an X86 compatilbe operating system which is multiboot compiled. It is written in C language (Visual studio code) and in assembly language. We are creating a docker image. buildenv: Our image , which is based on the already made gcc image tools, is created in a docker file that contains all the sets we need to create our build environment image. Docker simplies our process.
